Create Plan 6 - "Contact Form"
Plan Name: "Contact Form with Validation"
Plan Description:
Build a functional contact form with client-side validation and
server action for form submission.


Tasks:
Task 1: Contact Form Component
Create components/sections/Contact/ContactForm.tsx:
- Client component with form state
- Fields: name, email, phone, project type (dropdown), message
- Use shadcn Input, Textarea components
- Bronze submit button
- Loading state during submission
- Success/error messages

Task 2: Form Validation
Add validation to ContactForm:
- Required fields validation
- Email format validation
- Min length for message
- Display error messages below fields
- Disable submit until valid

Task 3: Server Action
Create app/actions/contact.ts:
- Server action to handle form submission
- Validate data server-side
- For now, console.log the data (later connect to email service)
- Return success/error response

Task 4: Contact Section
Create components/sections/Contact.tsx:
- Section heading: "Get in Touch"
- Subheading
- ContactForm component
- Optional: contact info sidebar (phone, email, address)
- Two column layout on desktop

Task 5: Add to Homepage

Update app/page.tsx:
- Add Contact section at bottom (before footer)